<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 14:01:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>更快的生物衰老可以解释年轻人癌症发病率的上升</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/faster-biological-aging-could-explain-rise-in-cancer-rates-in-younger-adults</link><description>一项新的研究表明，年轻一代的生物学衰老速度可能更快，从而增加了患早发癌症的风险。研究结果将较大的生物学年龄差距与癌症风险联系起来，凸显了预防癌症的新机会。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/faster-biological-aging-could-explain-rise-in-cancer-rates-in-younger-adults.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 14:01:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/faster-biological-aging-could-explain-rise-in-cancer-rates-in-younger-adults</guid></item><item><title>新型细菌冷却材料可以帮助电子产品和电动汽车电池运行温度更低</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/new-bacteria-based-cooling-material-could-help-electronics-and-ev-batteries-run-cooler</link><description>新一代电子设备（例如新型计算机和其他高功率设备）需要更多能量才能运行。当它们努力工作时，产生的强烈热量会限制它们的性能和可靠性。这就是为什么科学家们正在努力寻找更好、更可持续的材料来帮助冷却设备。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-bacteria-based-cooling-material-could-help-electronics-and-ev-batteries-run-cooler.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 13:46:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/new-bacteria-based-cooling-material-could-help-electronics-and-ev-batteries-run-cooler</guid></item><item><title>免疫系统的“和平使者”如何实现疾病的长期缓解</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/how-peacemakers-of-the-immune-system-could-unlock-long-term-disease-remission</link><description>一项新研究称，“和平缔造者”免疫细胞可以通过恢复免疫耐受来帮助治疗从 1 型糖尿病到神经退行性疾病等疾病&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/how-peacemakers-of-the-immune-system-could-unlock-long-term-disease-remission3.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 13:31:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/how-peacemakers-of-the-immune-system-could-unlock-long-term-disease-remission</guid></item><item><title>经典力学 — 问题 15 — 拉格朗日</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/classical-mechanics-problem-15-lagrangian</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 13:16:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/classical-mechanics-problem-15-lagrangian</guid></item><item><title>OpenAI 和 Broadcom 推出 LLM 优化的推理芯片</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/openai-and-broadcom-unveil-llm-optimized-inference-chip</link><description>OpenAI 和 Broadcom 推出 Jalapeo，这是一款专为 LLM 推理而构建的定制 AI 芯片，旨在提高 AI 系统的性能、效率和规模。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/openai-and-broadcom-unveil-llm-optimized-inference-chip.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 13:01:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/openai-and-broadcom-unveil-llm-optimized-inference-chip</guid></item><item><title>约翰·卡马克在桑迪·彼得森说“雷神之锤毁了 id 软件”后道歉，约翰·罗梅罗这一次没有告诉桑迪他错了</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/john-carmack-apologizes-after-sandy-petersen-says-quake-ruined-id-software-and-for-once-john-romero-doesnt-tell-sandy-hes-wrong</link><description>id Software 早期的三位负责人分享了一些略带伤感但最终令人振奋的对很久以前的回忆。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/john-carmack-apologizes-after-sandy-petersen-says-quake-ruined-id-software-and-for-once-john-romero-doesnt-tell-sandy-hes-wrong.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 12:46:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/john-carmack-apologizes-after-sandy-petersen-says-quake-ruined-id-software-and-for-once-john-romero-doesnt-tell-sandy-hes-wrong</guid></item><item><title>转变电子结构的计算主力</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/transforming-the-computational-workhorse-of-electronic-structure</link><description>时间相关密度泛函理论的几何重新表述可以更好地描述非平衡系统。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/transforming-the-computational-workhorse-of-electronic-structure2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 12:31:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/transforming-the-computational-workhorse-of-electronic-structure</guid></item><item><title>将低价值的金刚石粉尘转化为高性能量子材料</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/turning-low-value-diamond-dust-into-high-performance-quantum-materials</link><description>钻石长期以来因其美丽而受到人们的垂涎。其耀眼的色彩和净度使其成为奢华珠宝的完美候选者。然而，正是它们的其他独特特性，包括硬度、导热性和耐化学性，使钻石适合工业和先进技术中的各种应用。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/turning-low-value-diamond-dust-into-high-performance-quantum-materials.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 12:16:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/turning-low-value-diamond-dust-into-high-performance-quantum-materials</guid></item><item><title>激光实验推动氦气记录冲击压力</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/laser-experiments-push-helium-to-record-shock-pressures</link><description>在木星和土星等气态巨行星的深处，氢和氦在比地球大气层大数百万倍的压力下共存。在这些条件下，氦可能会与氢分离并影响行星的内部热流、结构和磁场。了解这些过程以及这些材料在极端条件下的行为对于建立准确的行星演化模型至关重要。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/laser-experiments-push-helium-to-record-shock-pressures.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 12:01:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/laser-experiments-push-helium-to-record-shock-pressures</guid></item><item><title>更长的激子寿命如何缓解有机太阳能电池的效率权衡</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/how-longer-exciton-lifetimes-could-ease-efficiency-trade-off-in-organic-solar-cells</link><description>尽管有机太阳能电池的效率目前已提升至20%以上，但由于物理限制，其性能难以进一步提升。来自瑞典林雪平大学、波茨坦大学、柏林保罗-德鲁德研究所和其他合作者的研究小组现已证明哪些物理过程限制了有机太阳能电池性能的关键参数。这为克服有机太阳能电池长期存在的效率限制提供了可能性。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/how-longer-exciton-lifetimes-could-ease-efficiency-trade-off-in-organic-solar-cells2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 11:46:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/how-longer-exciton-lifetimes-could-ease-efficiency-trade-off-in-organic-solar-cells</guid></item></channel></rss>